cloud.com/hkg-19</a><br />\n<br />\n係。。係吖。。打。。。打搞哂嗱。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔。。我知道嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但。。你唔怕我我係衰人黎嫁咩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ner 我。。。我可能會對你出。。。出手過wo..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呀。。。放心啦。。。我帶左黎嗱。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係喺e 個保溫壺入面嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我倒出黎俾你飲吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗱小心d 唔好倒瀉吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔。。。唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩。。。咩事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇理由個wo,我明明有個保溫壺載住個wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n哎吔～原來個保溫壺太耐冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能已經老化到保唔到溫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對。。。對唔住吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我。。。真係冇心嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係。。。你。。。懲罰我吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但。。。但我真係原諒唔到自己呀。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咦～e 到有條鞭wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係咁吖～你用黎鞭打我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎啦～你唔打我嘅話我唔安樂嫁～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔 我知道嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我保證你以後晚晚都飲到最溫暖嘅綠茶架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f133a3cbb04b52f5466972974573053d5fa908c","tid":627342,"uid":11314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:25:22.